snippet.title: Lesson Learned: Cult of the Elizabeth | Official Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Free prologue Lesson Learned: Cult of the Elizabeth is available today on Steam and Xbox.

You can now join Amelia and her classmates on a journey across the bizarre world of dreams, where a fight against bloodthirsty Countess Elizabeth Bathory awaits you!

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2252360
Xbox: https://www.xbox.com/games/store/lesson-learned-cult-of-the-elizabeth/9plkc6g3pfl8

Publisher Social Media: https://linktr.ee/gamingfactorysa
